main event: A UFO was observed flying at around 40,000 feet over Columbia Falls, Montana on September 16, 1967.
interesting points: The object was flying from east to west towards Whitefish, Montana.
The object was last seen going down east of the mountains, about 10-5 miles from Whitefish.
The object was seen flashing a light off and on, and had a white haze or smoke-like appearance underneath it.
The sighting lasted for approximately 4 minutes.
The report was made by two unnamed witnesses.
